            <sparkle:version>11</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.3.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>BlackBar 0.3.0</h2>
<ul>
<li>Menu facelift: the vCPU history renders as layered gradient areas instead of dense bars, legends become chip pills that only list statuses present in the window, and the raw Active/Queued/API/Updated text rows are replaced by a stats card with per-status history chips. The full API debug summary moves into the card&#x27;s tooltip.</li>
<li>Avoid rebuilding the SwiftUI status menu after background polling while the menu is closed, reducing idle CPU use.</li>
<li>Reuse ISO 8601 parsing styles while processing job history instead of rebuilding formatters for every timestamp.</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://github.com/steipete/BlackBar/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md">View full changelog</a></p>
]]></description>
