            <description><![CDATA[<h2>BlackBar 0.2.5</h2>
<ul>
<li>Treat an in-progress maintenance window as not operational, so the status stops reading &quot;All systems operational&quot; while the badge shows &quot;MAINT&quot;. Planned maintenance announced ahead of time stays operational until it actually starts. Thanks @devYRPauli.</li>
<li>Keep the website download buttons pointed at the latest GitHub release instead of a hard-coded older version.</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://github.com/steipete/BlackBar/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md">View full changelog</a></p>
]]></description>
